### ==========================================
### Create Order
### ==========================================

# REST Client variables
@host = http://localhost
@orderService = {{host}}:3000
@orderDapr = {{host}}:3500
@contentType = application/json

POST {{orderService}}/orders
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "orderId": "ORD-003",
    "amount": 100
}

###

### Create Another Order

POST {{orderService}}/orders
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "orderId": "ORD-101",
    "amount": 250
}

